{"tid":1520132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有事相求] 我媽今日突然成個人變囇 變咗藍絲","createTime":"2019-08-30T17:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:56:33.000Z","uid":314239,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ce166161bbc145526240b01792683abfb9a038c8","tid":1520132,"uid":314239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"我老母就最喜愛聽電台既<br />\n特別係翻工嗰陣大大聲播<br />\n本身我都睇死佢一定撐警<br />\n所以喺運動剛開始嗰陣冇同佢傾過政治野<br />\n直到有一日佢睇住CCTVB<br />\n拍枱屌爆林鄭<br />\n我先同佢傾下呢個運動啲新聞<br />\n佢係十分理智既黃絲<br />\n會屌林鄭<br />\n會屌啲鬼<br />\n會屌班大陸智障兒<br />\n即使佢知屌完自己啲三姑六婆會冇親戚做都未怕過<br />\n甚至佢係銅鑼灣之前有講過佢覺得有鬼混入<br />\n琴日讚我地大埔連儂隧道同其他連儂牆貼得好靚<br />\n被人撕完又貼好勁等等等等<br />\n<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢今日一翻到黎<br />\n我話沙田大圍嗰邊有好多人大叫口號呀<br />\n然後佢一野彈句<br />\n你唔好咁多事理人地！<br />\n你得閒冇野做？<br />\n唔好出去行完俾人影大頭<br />\n工都冇得翻！<br />\n以前佔中嗰啲後悔去抗爭搞到冇咗份工啊！<br />\n搞到要翻大陸揾工！你想翻大陸？<br />\n以後唔準出！<br />\n然後狂屌我去遊行乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n我頂唔順同佢嘈咗<br />\n包括<br />\n其他人講你又信？<br />\n我睇嗰啲有證有據你就人云亦云<br />\n佔中嗰啲係義士！我地一定唔會俾佢地失業！有好多人支援佢地！（其實亂講，不過俾著係我都唔會當義士condom!!!!!!!)<br />\n下刪千字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我嚴重懷疑電台有大量藍絲phone inn /comment扭曲事實<br />\n搞到佢聽完好似變咗另一個人咁</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我希望大家可以同我一齊！<br />\nPhone in+留言去電台&amp;佢地fb page<br />\n我地唔係要佢地接收洗腦資訊<br />\n我地喺要俾佢地知道依家香港發生幾大件事<br />\n好多你想像唔到會發生既事都係真既！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我相信我老母會變<br />\n其他都會變！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求幫推！求求大家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831 901 見！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5194e77ac746b3198371e1fa96e7341ac30a5c","tid":1520132,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=01fa2020\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=68fa758c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2RphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=9ffa9849\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"868247fb16ac0b18a2207fe17ffabf9c2341d092","tid":1520132,"uid":72034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"咁易變就唔係理智黃絲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4902a4b230ec19819db99c7bc434930c578c28a","tid":1520132,"uid":187510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"佢似係俾白色恐怖嚇到 唔想你受害"},{"pid":"879f882975e07a97ccbf53fb028006c7f732b109","tid":1520132,"uid":270956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4902a4b230ec19819db99c7bc434930c578c28a",